{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4cfd1447ff","title":"接见以苏班德里约为首的印度尼西亚代表团时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e0d615a432","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"4cfd1447ff","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cedbdb9690","type":"title","text":"接见以苏班德里约为首的印度尼西亚代表团时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c48903e68","type":"paragraph","text":"接见以苏班德里约为首的印尼代表团时的讲话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73493f0e8c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0b7d91f78","type":"paragraph","text":"1965.01.27","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73b5a9ca16","type":"paragraph","text":"好的拿来，坏的丢掉。无论是本国的或外国的都一样，只能批判地接受，不能教条主义，照搬。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"090aad3820","type":"paragraph","text":"军事学校办得一塌糊涂，正在整理。过去没有军事学校可好了。打了几十年仗，就是没有军事学校。我们的军队百分之九十以上是不识字和小学程度的。国民党尽办军事学校，什么陆军大学毕业，就是我们这些不识字的兵打倒了它。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c4e944455","type":"paragraph","text":"进军事学校的时间太长了。蒋介石办的黄埔军校，两个月入伍训练，四个月学校毕业。蒋介石的军队主要就是这些人还比较能打，陆军大学毕业的实在不能打。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06794c0d18","type":"paragraph","text":"书可以读一些，但是读多了害人，的确害人。革命斗争培养干部。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4cfd1447ff","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}